                     <interp inst="t18290409-275-person2517" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. The prisoner was brought to me; the handkerchief was delivered to me by Harris.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-275-person2518">
                  JOHN 
                  HARRIS
               <interp inst="t18290409-275-person2518" type="surname" value="HARRIS"></interp>
